{"tid":232605,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樂視走數】3香港指樂視拖欠網絡服務費多時","createTime":"2017-05-07T00:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T10:35:27.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20de3f9938286dd768c352f70c52b628196763cb","tid":232605,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/084549_0180788fa8199eb01ac44879bedb4158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F084549_0180788fa8199eb01ac44879bedb4158.jpg&h=720ee11d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3香港及3家居寬頻今日首次透露，樂視拖欠和記環球電訊網絡服務費多時，要求樂視盡早繳清有關欠款及履行合約條款。樂視公關回覆本報查詢時指，目前正了解事件中，暫未有回應。3香港公關未有透露樂視欠款金額，以及拖欠達多長時間，亦不回應公司會否採取法律行動追討。<br />\n<br />\n和記環球電訊網絡為樂視雲計算（與樂視體育香港同屬集團的公司）其中一個電訊服務供應商，3香港指出，該公司拖欠和記環球電訊的服務費多時，期間已多次主動與樂視雲計算及樂視體育香港接洽，尋求不影響客戶服務的解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n3香港又指，發現昨晚大約午夜12時起未能觀看樂視體育香港的節目，及一度未能登入樂視體育香港的網站。公司隨即透過不同渠道與樂視體育香港跟進有關情況，隨後至今早9時半發現服務陸續回復正常。3香港強調，公司的流動網絡及固網服務一直運作正常，在該時段並無任何故障，故服務受影響與公司的網絡絕對無關。<br />\n<br />\n3香港公關向本報確認，受影響節目包括今日凌晨3時「韋斯咸：熱刺」英超賽事，他續指，公司有收到客戶致電話查詢訊號故障問題，未透露具體投訴數字。另據樂視體育節目表，受影響賽事包括今日早上7時一場NBA賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56659791&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56659791%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170506&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=f08e2946\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56659791%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170506&h=ef4587c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56659791&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170506</a><br />\n<br />\n//呢次你仲唔冚家剷.jpg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e63caf01c16f320db5fae3b7cd3cb86ac6b20ed","tid":232605,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:50:41.000Z","msg":"傳用家仍未能提現　易到用車重申：月內解決問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/084957_339c10fdf6f5569f1a0af700e27aedbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F084957_339c10fdf6f5569f1a0af700e27aedbc.jpg&h=c86ea0e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂視子公司、Call車App「易到用車」陷入財政困境，至上月末，公司表示融資進展順利，料於月內解決司機提款問題。內地《新京報》報道，市傳昨日（5日）為易到解決提現問題的截止日，惟有數十名司機去到易到總部，他們均表示交易後未能提現，金額由數百至數萬元（人民幣．下同）不等。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，有司機未能當場完成提現，需在16個工作日之後才能收到錢，亦有司機反映，已完成的訂單無法結算，收入亦未到賬。<br />\n<br />\n《新京報》表示，上月25日，市傳易到將會每日提供300萬元資金供提現，並承諾在本月5日前解決提款問題。報道指，易到內部公關昨晚澄清，傳聞僅屬「謠言」，公司從未公佈解決問題之具體時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56659044&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56659044%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170506&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=f41f8548\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56659044%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170506&h=a7c9244b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56659044&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170506</a>"},{"pid":"1810d93787f368d5f27f31a23e3b41b0c8e367fa","tid":232605,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"支那野，無好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be9839950a7bdfe48c2fbc505384501e3696364","tid":232605,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT